PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772640680
OL,3,CUnderwater searches being carried out
OL,4,Cfor missing woman from Bradford
OL,6,FMrs Hiles, a former police officer,
OL,7,Fnow works as a dog groomer and
OL,8,Fregularly walks in the Apperley Bridge
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FItems belonging to Jane were found on
OL,12,Fthe riverbank on the south side of the
OL,13,Friver near Apperley Road on Thursday,
OL,14,F26 February.
OL,16,FMrs Hiles is described as white, slim,
OL,17,F5ft 4ins tall, with blonde, short
OL,18,Fspikey hair and was wearing a long
OL,19,Fblack coat.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
