PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772640680
OL,3,CUnderwater searches being carried out
OL,4,Cfor missing woman from Bradford
OL,6,FIt is understood that she had planned
OL,7,Fa holiday to Peru in April.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Rachel McKay, of
OL,10,FBradford CID, said: "We are continuing
OL,11,Fto support Jane's family and keep them
OL,12,Fupdated while our searches to find her
OL,13,Fare progressing.
OL,15,F"We are working with our specialist
OL,16,Fsearch advisers and other partners,
OL,17,Fsuch as mountain rescue volunteers, to
OL,18,Fcontinue our searches of the land and
OL,19,Fwaterways in the area.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
