PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772640680
OL,3,CUnderwater searches being carried out
OL,4,Cfor missing woman from Bradford
OL,6,F"The possible sighting in Buck Wood,
OL,7,FThackley, on the day she went missing
OL,8,Fis unconfirmed, but we would like to
OL,9,Fhear from anyone who has seen her in
OL,10,Fthat area or anywhere else in the
OL,11,Fvicinity."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
